1. Executive Summary
The e-commerce platform successfully recorded 4.92M in total revenue from 5000 distinct orders, equating to 11K total items sold. The platform demonstrates strong seasonal trends with significant sales peaks early in the year.
2. Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)
Metric	Value
Total Orders	5000
Total Revenue	4.92M
Total Quantity Sold	11K
Total Discounts Applied	124.26K
3. Financial Performance and Trends
Monthly Sales Volume (Quantity)
Sales quantity peaked in February (1473 units), dipped significantly in the mid-year (April-June), and showed a slight recovery towards December (807 units).
Monthly Revenue Trends (Month Wise Sales Trending)
Revenue followed a similar pattern, with the highest months generating around 0.60M, while lower months generated around 0.26M.
