5. Customer Demographics & Behavior
Top 10 Customers (by Max Page View & Purchase)
Customer acquisition seems strong, with several customers (CUST 03232, CUST 02567, etc.) consistently engaging with the platform.
Geographic Insights
Istanbul is the leading market, contributing significantly to revenue (1.1M) and maintaining an average delivery time of 6.6 days.
Device Usage and Payment
Most Used Device: Mobile devices are likely the top device type based on general e-commerce trends and volume metrics shown in the dashboard visuals.
Preferred Payment: Credit Card is the dominant payment method (39% of transactions).
